sentence: More than 50 House Republicans were at a Washington, D.C., fundraiser on Wednesday night for Harriet Hageman, Rep. Liz Cheney's challenger in Wyoming.
author: Aaron Navarro
title: Over 50 House Republicans attend fundraiser for Liz Cheney's challenger, Harriet Hageman
